.Dd September 15, 2019
.Dt MOUNT_ZFS 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm mount_zfs
.Nd helper utility for mounting legacy ZFS mounts
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar ZFS_dataset
.Ar mount_point
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility supports mounting ZFS filesystems via /etc/fstab where the ZFS property is mountpoint=legacy.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr fstab 5 ,
.Xr zfs 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
utility first appeared in
.Nx 9.0 .
